title: Dublin Tech Circuit Pilot Event
description: The event saw 66 students, across 9 different tech teams, with Drimnagh Castle team winning the overall title. The pilot event included STEM based activities. The success of the event strengthened our vision of Dublin Tech Circuit.

title: Dublin Tech Circuit Annual Challenge 2024
description: Over 100 students participated in various robotics and programming challenges, pushing the limits of innovation and teamwork.
